    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it compulsory to put lights on when driving on motorways when it is raining",
        "additional_details": "Because there is a massive safety issue whilst driving in the rain during the day with no lights on. The spray from big vehicles is a major hazard. If some vehicles are not showing lights it is sometimes very hard to see them.",
        "background": "Change the law to make it compulsory for motorists to put lights on whilst driving in the rain on all UK motorways.",
